subject: [Info] CouchSurfing may share aggregated or anonymized information that does not directly identify you.
text:
"We may also share aggregated or anonymized information that does not
directly identify you."

i guess this is ok as long as it's really true, and depending on how
you define 'directly'. If the stats that are shared can really not be
tracked back to you, then i guess it doesn't affect your privacy?
